{"serial": "63024", "department_serial": 59, "code": "SS6005", "class": "A", "name": {"en": "Special Topics Ⅰ", "ch": "專題研究Ⅰ"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Pan, Chen-Jeih"], "ch": ["潘貞杰"]}, "credits": 1, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 1, "session": ["3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "S4", "room": "810"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "太空科學與工程學系", "en": "Department of Space Science and Engineering"}, "system": {"ch": "碩士班", "en": "Master Programs"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 0, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "由於太陽能比例的上升，太陽輻射的變異在發展強韌的電力系統中發揮著重要作用。由於雲層引起的陽光遮蔽是影響太陽輻射的主要因素。為了達成輻射預報的目標，在本研究中採用基於相位相關的自適應跟踪算法來實現這一目標。", "en": "The obscuration of sunlight caused by clouds is the main factor that reduces solar power generated. Therefore, solar irradiance forecasts are essential in constructing a resilient power grid. In the present study, a sunlight obscuration event (SOE) is defined as a cloud obscuring the sun in the sky, representing the reduction of direct sunlight, and solar power generation is expected to decrease."}, "outline": {"ch": "本研究利用由全天空影像導出的雲速度，使用地面風速進行品質驗證。當得出此刻雲的位移速度時，利用此一速度當基準，透過平均進行三十分鐘內的雲分布預測，進一步推算該地的輻射量，並與歷史資料做比對，驗證其輻射預測能力。", "en": "An all-sky imager monitors the cloud distribution in the whole sky. Further cloud motions are derived from all-sky images (ASIs) using an adaptive tracking algorithm based on phase correlation. The derived cloud motions are used to predict sky areas obscured by clouds, and a 10-minute SOE forecast is thus made, providing crucial information on immediate solar irradiance for power dispatch and grid operation. Forecast validation will also be introduced in this presentation."}, "textbook": {"ch": "journal papers", "en": "journal papers"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "0", "en": "0"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n\n實習/實驗\n個別指導", "en": ["Lecture", "", "Practical Training Lab", "Individual Instruction"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "report 100％", "en": "report 100％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "Tue 34", "en": "Tue 34"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "高層大氣科學與電離層物理", "en": "高層大氣科學與電離層物理"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "太空科學知識的建立", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現", "學習檔案評量", "自我評量/同儕互評", "作品/創作展演", "其他"]}, {"competencies": "日地系統觀測技術的培養", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現", "學習檔案評量", "自我評量/同儕互評", "作品/創作展演", "其他"]}, {"competencies": "整合創新與獨立思考", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現", "學習檔案評量", "自我評量/同儕互評", "作品/創作展演", "其他"]}, {"competencies": "資料分析能力的養成", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現", "學習檔案評量", "自我評量/同儕互評", "作品/創作展演", "其他"]}, {"competencies": "數值模式的應用", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現", "學習檔案評量", "自我評量/同儕互評", "作品/創作展演", "其他"]}, {"competencies": "研究結果的表達及呈現", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現", "學習檔案評量", "自我評量/同儕互評", "作品/創作展演", "其他"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Buildup of Space science knowledge", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance", "Portfolios Assessment", "Self Assessment/ Peer Assessment", "Products/Creative Performance", "Others"]}, {"competencies": "Cultivation of Solar-Terrestrial observation technology", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance", "Portfolios Assessment", "Self Assessment/ Peer Assessment", "Products/Creative 